name: Sophrosyne Cards set#1 "Reflections"
description: Twitter.com/EDMrSprinkles: Each Limited Edition series of cards will be designed from a "Muse" card.This will be a photograph from my personal portfolio & will be edgy, thought provoking, as well as a visceral connection to our humanity. First series stems from a 2013 flood photo that has helped me better understand this human experiment & accept some things aren't meant to be understood. "Reflections" is about finding the courage & wherewithal to know when self introspection is needed. This series features 8 different cards w/words of inspiration & empowerment.
